name: Kristanna Loken
description:
Kristanna Sommer Loken is a Norwegian-American actress best known for portraying the T-X Terminator in Terminator 3. She has also acted for a few other projects but by the looks of it, it seems best they are left entirely unmentioned. I decided to embed her after making a LORA of Kristanna as the T-X.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. I've noticed with some models it might be necessary to use increased token weight to get backgrounds or settings to render properly.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
